{"tid":300143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英女皇訪問香港 VS  習種怕港獨 動員1萬黑警戒嚴","createTime":"2017-06-27T15:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T01:30:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17dc36e169f47d26fe1089bf0a3e11009df7f9d8","tid":300143,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"事頭婆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thosewerethedays.files.wordpress.com/2012/06/2012-06-29_055524.jpg?w=490&amp;h=366\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthosewerethedays.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F06%2F2012-06-29_055524.jpg%3Fw%3D490%26h%3D366&h=dc19a4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/07/55/10075597_912301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F07%2F55%2F10075597_912301.jpg&h=33946e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/07/55/10075598_148319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F07%2F55%2F10075598_148319.jpg&h=838d5e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">警方預留近萬人手應對習近平訪港 將設保安區禁止市民出入</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170627/large/27la2p15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F27la2p15.jpg&h=e60ef94f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1840000/1843835/security_exmobile_20170626_c_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1840000%2F1843835%2Fsecurity_exmobile_20170626_c_1024.png&h=0ba9dc51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平周四訪港3天，警方將預留近萬人手應對。警方指，如發生任何突發事件，會按既定程序處理，又強調會有足夠人手應付。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，會在習近平的活動範圍附近設置保安區，禁止市民出入。同時，由於部份行程可能因應情況有所變動，保安部署亦會不斷更新，警方會盡量減輕對市民影響。"},{"pid":"53b807567aad62fad31fd6051a77468a2dd5d6d1","tid":300143,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"不如戒嚴啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc597793cd098cbd28665d2e592f72fddfc9f69","tid":300143,"uid":56430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:54:48.000Z","msg":"胡錦濤來香港嗰次<br />\n個入境處女職員連普通話都唔識講<br />\n起碼叫做唔係做戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0631bd381a753ec10998932a2e46194deb4c5ad","tid":300143,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"此一時彼一時<br />\n已經係上世紀既事, 公道d 點比較<br />\n始終成個世界格局已經唔同<br />\n<br />\n不過攪到咁, 不如全部香港人放幾日假算<br />\n起碼街上減少左一班返工, 返學既人走黎走去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e01c27ba14eb4b7be47fc1360cc17cff07eab1","tid":300143,"uid":35135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"出國都無咁勁，<br />\n喺香港，所謂自己嘅地方，仲多人想隊佢？"},{"pid":"37c488cb8ff574d8ba1150afa89872ae46e77fe8","tid":300143,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此一時彼一時<br />\n已經係上世紀既事, 公道d 點比較<br />\n始終成個世界格局已經唔同<br />\n<br />\n不過攪到咁, 不如全部香港人放幾日假算<br />\n起碼街上減少左一班返工, 返學既人走黎走去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世界格局有乜唔同 ?<br />\n<br />\n擺明係得罪人, 民心啦<br />\n<br />\n廢話得你"},{"pid":"04de44f99f297f300bc3dae99ee955c7950a91bb","tid":300143,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出國都無咁勁，<br />\n喺香港，所謂自己嘅地方，仲多人想隊佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕港獨怕得要命"},{"pid":"96999e2ee886f88e6aafb901a9492aa6f45bbab4","tid":300143,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>此